workspace.name:
biorefinerySize: biorefinerySize[production_]:=Round[Which[
    production < 2000*365*0.9,
    production/(250*365*0.9),
    production < 5000*365*0.9,
    production/(5000*365*0.9),
    True,
    production/(2000*365*0.9)
],1]

workspace.name:
stover: stover = Select[county, #[[4]] == "Corn" &][[1;;]] //
    Map[AssociationThread[headers[[All, 2]], #] &] //
    Map[<|
    "fips"->#["fips"], 
    "County"->#["County"],
    "State"->#["State"],
    "Production"->#["Production"]*56/2205.0, (* convert bu/year to tonnes/year*)
    "Land Area"->#["Land Area"], 
    "Biomass Price"->#["Biomass Price"],
    "Biorefineries" -> biorefinerySize[#["Production"]*56/2205.0] (* 2000 tonne per day pyrolysis*)
    |> &]
